WorkItem.Description: Hello. I imported datas from battle.net armory to Rawr 5.0.5. When they all came to rawr, the dps stats for items are not shown in the right side panel. Only old and low item level items (cata) dps stats are shown. There is MoP items but there are not dps stat per item. Even it is not shown what to enchant or reforge.

Comments.Message: Unfortunately, I do not know the state of Elemental Shaman in Rawr and I do not know if anyone is actively working on it.  Be sure to check the release notes to see if there are any elemental shaman updates.
The elemental module is completely outdated and non-functional.
